Package: ggcall.example
Title: Example Implementation of 'ggcall'
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person("Maciej", "Nasinski", , "nasinski.maciej@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Example implementation of 'ggcall' which enhances the functionality of ggplot2 by enabling users to retrieve the complete code used to generate a ggplot object inside a function. 
    The 'ggcall' package is beneficial for understanding and replicating complex ggplot2 plots returned by a function. 
License: Apache License (>= 2)
